,'文章分类状态','POST','/adminapi/article.articleCate/updateStatus','[{\"id\":8}]','','223.104.161.230',1753454383),(143,1,'admin','','文章分类状态','POST','/adminapi/article.articleCate/updateStatus','[{\"id\":5}]','','223.104.161.230',1753454383),(144,1,'admin','','文章分类状态','POST','/adminapi/article.articleCate/updateStatus','[{\"id\":9}]','','223.104.161.230',1753454383),(145,1,'admin','','文章分类状态','POST','/adminapi/article.articleCate/updateStatus','[{\"id\":6}]','','223.104.161.230',1753454383),(146,1,'admin','','文章分类状态','POST','/adminapi/article.articleCate/updateStatus','[{\"id\":7}]','','223.104.161.230',1753454383),(147,1,'admin','','文章分类状态','POST','/adminapi/article.articleCate/updateStatus','[{\"id\":4}]','','223.104.161.230',1753454383),(148,1,'admin','','文章状态','POST','/adminapi/article.article/updateStatus','[{\"id\":4}]','','223.104.161.230',1753454459),(149,1,'admin','','文章新增','POST','/adminapi/article.article/add','[{\"abstract\":\"\",\"author\":\"admin\",\"cid\":6,\"click_virtual\":0,\"content\":\"<p><strong>一、[Err] 42000 - [SQL Server]“offset”附近有语法错误。42000 - [SQL Server]在 FETCH 语句中选项 NEXT 的用法无效。</strong></p><p> 1、版本问题</p><p>   sqlserver2012及之后的版本</p><p> 2、必须有order by</p><p><img src=\\\"../jeecgboot/sys/common/static/jeditor/blobid24_1730038569900.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"\\\"/></p><p><strong>二、Error getting generated key or setting result to parameter object, cause: Error</strong></p><p> 可能是数据库ID自增的问题，mybait又设置了值</p><p><strong>三、sqlserver当IDENTITY_INSERT设置为OFF时，不能为表‘XXX‘ 中的标识列插入显式值</strong></p><p><img src=\\\"../jeecgboot/sys/common/static/jeditor/blobid25_1730038651965.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"\\\"/></p><p><img src=\\\"../jeecgboot/sys/common/static/jeditor/blobid26_1730038652023.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"\\\"/></p><p><strong>四、sqlserver多次为 \'totalData\' 指定了列 \'EmpGuid</strong>\'</p><p><img src=\\\"../jeecgboot/sys/common/static/jeditor/mceclip2_1730038696168.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"\\\"/></p><p><strong>五、sqlserver无法连接</strong></p><p><img src=\\\"../jeecgboot/sys/common/static/jeditor/blobid27_1730038723962.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"\\\"/></p><p> 如果是内网服务器，使用内网连接，而不是公网</p><p><strong>六、解决sql server保存对象字符串转换成uniqueidentifier失败的问题</strong></p><p> 使用UUID带-形式</p><p><strong>七、数据查询特别慢的问题</strong></p><p><img src=\\\"../jeecgboot/sys/common/static/jeditor/blobid28_1730038821357.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"\\\"/></p><p> 可能类型原因，不去查这个字段</p><p><strong>八、sqlServer ------com.microsoft.sqlserver.jdbc.SQLServerException: 必须执行该语句才能获得结果</strong></p><p> mybatis plus非sql使用sqlserver新增有问题</p><p><img src=\\\"../jeecgboot/sys/common/static/jeditor/blobid29_1730038925977.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"\\\"/></p><p> 自定义id不行，不指定id，打印sql id为空</p><p><img src=\\\"../jeecgboot/sys/common/static/jeditor/blobid30_1730038926041.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"\\\"/></p><p><img src=\\\"../jeecgboot/sys/common/static/jeditor/blobid31_1730038925992.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"\\\"/></p><p><img src=\\\"../jeecgboot/sys/common/static/jeditor/blobid32_1730038925999.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"\\\"/></p><p> mybatis sql 不写id</p><p><br></p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p>\",\"desc\":\"SQLServer常见问题\",\"image\":\"\",\"isShow\":1,\"sort\":0,\"title\":\"SQLServer常见问题\"}]','','223.104.161.230',1753454491),(150,1,'admin','','文章状态','POST','/adminapi/article.article/updateStatus','[{\"id\":4}]','','223.104.161.230',1753454491),(151,1,'admin','','文章编辑','POST','/adminapi/article.article/edit','[{\"abstract\":\"\",\"author\":\"admin\",\"cid\":6,\"click_virtual\":0,\"content\":\"<p><strong>一、[Err] 42000 - [SQL Server]“offset”附近有语法错误。42000 - [SQL Server]在 FETCH 语句中选项 NEXT 的用法无效。</strong></p><p> 1、版本问题</p><p> &nbsp; sqlserver2012及之后的版本</p><p> 2、必须有order by</p><p><img src=\\\"http://zy.wlown.com/adminapi/uploads/image/20250725/98a9dfd4-5448-4bcd-8289-db79e7200850.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"\\\"/></p><p><strong>二、Error getting generated key or setting result to parameter object, cause: Error</strong></p><p> 可能是数据库ID自增的问题，mybait又设置了值</p><p><strong>三、sqlserver当IDENTITY_INSERT设置为OFF时，不能为表‘XXX‘ 中的标识列插入显式值</strong></p><p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"../jeecgboot/sys/common/static/jeditor/blobid25_1730038651965.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"\\\"><img src=\\\"http://zy.wlown.com/adminapi/uploads/image/20250725/2250fea9-c217-4c1d-a820-3c8892ff39b7.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"\\\"></p><p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"../jeecgboot/sys/common/static/jeditor/blobid26_1730038652023.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"\\\"><img src=\\\"http://zy.wlown.com/adminapi/uploads/image/20250725/486bbfac-90a3-4da5-abe9-fe9d14ced0da.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"width: 643.00px;height: 310.12px;\\\"></p><p><strong>四、sqlserver多次为 \'totalData\' 指定了列 \'EmpGuid</strong>\'</p><p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"../jeecgboot/sys/common/static/jeditor/mceclip2_1730038696168.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"\\\"><img src=\\\"http://zy.wlown.com/adminapi/uploads/image/20250725/e0df43ef-9551-4ba5-8c31-55aa168fd777.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"width: 645.00px;height: 632.89px;\\\"></p><p><strong>五、sqlserver无法连接</strong></p><p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img src=\\\"../jeecgboot/sys/common/static/jeditor/blobid27_1730038723962.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"\\\"><img src=\\\"http://zy.wlown.com/adminapi/uploads/image/20250725/80bd5942-57d3-44e4-a24a-af1c44c9200a.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" data-href=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"width: 767.00px;height: 202.70px;\\\"></p><p> 如果是内网服务器，使用内网连接，而不是公网</p><p><strong>六、解决sql server保存对象字符串转换成uniqueidentifier失败的问题</strong></p><p> 使用UUID带-形式</p><p><strong>七、数据查询特别慢的问题</strong></p><p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">